org.usfirst.frc.team4500.robot

Class RobotMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.usfirst.frc.team4500.robot.RobotMap

  • public class RobotMap
extends java.lang.Object
    Use the RobotMap for storing the port numbers of all of our motors and sensors as well as any other constants which may be subject to change. Never hard code port numbers! Reference the variables here so they may be changed on the fly while we build the robot.
